sentences.english: The court in Deyang declined to comment.

sentences.english: The well field of Xinchang is situated in the interior of Deyang of Sichuan province.

sentences.english: In terms of prediction result, one exploration well was deployed in Deyang Syncline.
sentences.chinese: 根据预测结果，在德阳向斜部署了一口探井。

sentences.english: Wenchuan affected by the earthquake, Deyang City, Sichuan Province East steam secondary school buildings collapsed.
sentences.chinese: 受汶川地震影响，四川省德阳市东汽中学教学楼坍塌。
